<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَمَنْ كَانَتْ الدُّنْيَا قُصَارَى مُرَادِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَقَدْ بَاءَ بالْخُسْرَانِ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَمَنْ لَمْ يَكُنْ فِي طَاعَةِ اللهِ شُغْلُهُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عَلَى كُلِّ حَالٍ لا يَفُوزُ بِبُغْيَةِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمَنْ أَكْثَرُ الْعِصْيَانِ مِنْ غَيْرِ تَوْبَةٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَذَاكَ طَرِيحٌ فِي فَيَافِي الْغِوَايَةِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بَعِيدٌ مِنَ الْخَيْرَاتِ حَلَّ بِهِ الْبَلا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَوَاجَهَهُ الْخُذْلانُ مِنْ كُلِّ وِجْهَةِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>عَجِبْتُ لِمَنْ يُوصِي سِوَاهُ وَإِنَّهُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>لأَجْدَرُ مِنْهُ بِاتِّبَاعِ الْوَصِيَّةِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>يَقُولُ بِلا فِعْلٍ وَيَعْلَمُ عَامِلاً<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عَلَى ضِدِّ عِلْمٍ يَا لَهَا مِنْ خَسَارَةِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>عُلُومٌ كَأَمْثَالِ الْجِبَالِ تَلاطَمَتْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَأَعْمَالُهُ فِي جَنْبِهَا مِثْلُ قَطْرَةِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَقَدْ أَنْفَقَ الأَيَّامَ فِي غَيْرِ طَائِلٍ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>كَمِثْل اللَّيَالِي إِذَا تَقَضَّتْ وَوَلَّتِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>عَلَى السَّوْفِ وَالتَّسْوِيفِ شَرُّ مُصَاحِبٍ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَقَوْلِ عَسَى عَنْ فَتْرَةِ وَبَطَالَةِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>تَنَكَّبَ عَجْزًا عَنْ طَرِيقِ عَزِيمَةٍ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَمَالَ لِتَأْوِيلٍ ضَعِيفٍ وَرُخْصَةِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>